{"tid":1530309,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁美芬建議參考英國成立非法定調查委員會查找政府不足","createTime":"2019-09-02T02:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T03:58:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"838b7c3c0f3d069584f355766cd442aeb62cdc29","tid":1530309,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:25:35.000Z","msg":"經民聯立法會議員梁美芬表示，周末多區警民衝突令人憂慮，暴力令很多人恐慌。她認為一定要和暴力劃清界線，反對派亦應該清晰表示不應再用暴力。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬在本台節目《千禧年代》表示，各界集中在警民衝突，而警隊是執法部門，一旦香港出現嚴重暴力，不論動機都要執法，而個別懷疑使用過分武力的情況，可以按制度處理。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬建議參考英國經驗，成立非法定的調查委員會，查找政府、立法機關和教育制度等的不足。她認為不應糾結在調查形式。至於示威者會否接受，梁美芬說要視乎雙方主導輿論者的意見，又說示威者很多是年輕人，質疑有多少人了解過《調查委員會條例》。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478319-20190902.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1478319-20190902.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2Fdkum%2F%2B3HP0Ta45uqRfUpIg%3D&h=9bde9295\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1478319-20190902.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d72099a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478319-20190902.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e6822bb1fe68aa6a7b3f9ef4d4291cfd54bd0229","tid":1530309,"uid":56729,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:26:55.000Z","msg":"又到左選舉既時候 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1462ab001122a7f64682d21089244125dade353","tid":1530309,"uid":188176,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:27:28.000Z","msg":"非法定的調查委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797750c48af1857b5e22d4dc00932c41afeb53bc","tid":1530309,"uid":219564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:27:52.000Z","msg":"建議9月8日百萬人大遊行，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案，宣揚攬炒精神﹗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1510235\